cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.AI, cs.DS

The paper discusses a new proof-of-work scheme for a cryptocurrency running over a blockchain that involves training deep learning models. This falls under the category of cryptography (cs.CR) as well as machine learning (cs.LG) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the democratization of access to artificial intelligence, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS).
